# Git workflow

After **any** task-related edits (code, config, assets, project rules — anything that should land in the repo), **create a git commit** before ending the turn. Message: clear, conventional-style subject; optional body with complete sentences when helpful.

The **user runs `git push`** — do **not** run `git push` unless they explicitly ask you to push.
